### Contributors
* @brianherman,  gui
* @sclevel2 Spencer Cleveland, bfs algorithm

### How to download
Download the code from the zip file on the right.
### How to Run
Run the jar in the zip file to run.
### How to play
Pieces move in the opposite direction of where you click and drag. It takes getting used to but it works.
